title: Google\Cloud\Datastream\V1\BigQueryDestinationConfig\SourceHierarchyDatasets\DatasetTemplate
name: DatasetTemplate
description:
Dataset template used for dynamic dataset creation.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.datastream.v1.BigQueryDestinationConfig.SourceHierarchyDatasets.DatasetTemplate

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.location
params.description: Required. The geographic location where the dataset should reside. See https://cloud.google.com/bigquery/docs/locations for supported locations.

params.name: data.dataset_id_prefix
params.description: If supplied, every created dataset will have its name prefixed by the provided value. The prefix and name will be separated by an underscore. i.e. _.

params.name: data.kms_key_name
params.description: Describes the Cloud KMS encryption key that will be used to protect destination BigQuery table. The BigQuery Service Account associated with your project requires access to this encryption key. i.e. projects/{project}/locations/{location}/keyRings/{key_ring}/cryptoKeys/{cryptoKey}. See https://cloud.google.com/bigquery/docs/customer-managed-encryption for more information.
